{"tid":2400062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"感染武肺可唔可以成為新既抗爭方式？","createTime":"2021-02-08T15:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T03:23:40.000Z","uid":273621,"like":11,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"53f8d9d8edfeffab4359bb0f2c94f9bde746ed80","tid":2400062,"uid":273621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T15:21:37.000Z","msg":"係人都知封唔封區同每日確診數字無咩關係<br />\n政府係想搭順風車宣傳強硬獨裁管治方式有效率姐<br />\n<br />\n假如我地揾方法推返高個確診數字，政府咪無得freeride市民抗疫成果，可以證明中共個套獨裁管治方式係不切實際lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尤其年青力壯，中左都係病幾日發下燒<br />\n同2019年上街示威既風險根本無得比<br />\n整病自己黎證明政府管治失敗都係攬炒姐<br />\n<br />\n當然，屋企有老人家/長期病患者就千祈唔好亂試，死亡率高好多<br />\n<br />\n可以叫：<span class=\"xx-large\">和你病</span><br />\n點睇？"},{"pid":"b50bc2de4c5c1f66a40230c83c9b3de6ae911208","tid":2400062,"uid":55851,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T15:24:26.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"94e9eeee0f71cbcbf588e297be0b0072ea6d8599","tid":2400062,"uid":62259,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T15:25:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MjTQL4R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMjTQL4R.jpg&h=f1446ed6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89260a7518526f89a5a59fead9c9aec39d0094e0","tid":2400062,"uid":250491,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T15:28:37.000Z","msg":"證明到又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全部人搞到身體差晒<br />\n有晒後遺症都改變唔到d咩<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"3ce8e3724a4dd178947834a485b4d02380e9378f","tid":2400062,"uid":273621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T15:30:34.000Z","msg":"和你病<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779296535a7ea721b5e310413930546f2d1b660f","tid":2400062,"uid":247896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T15:31:06.000Z","msg":"和你sick"},{"pid":"93a119bf080fb393df49704244f2134a4e4c42d3","tid":2400062,"uid":27362